data.description: FULL BASEMENT and 3 CAR GARAGE plus BRAND NEW ROOF on 4000+ SF House featuring 5BD, 4BA, LOFT, Game Room, Entertainment Area, Private Front Porch, Screened-in Back Patio has Ceiling Fan, chairs & more. Brand New Roof installed September 2023 with 5-star coverage (50 year roof shingle warranty). 5" upgraded Hardwood Floor cover the main level. Upgraded Kitchen w/42" Toasted Antique Cabinets, beautiful White Ornamental Granite Countertops w/Tiled Backsplash, Large Island, Double Wall Ovens & SS Appliances. Opens to Family Room w/Stacked Stone Fireplace. Dual Bookshelves can for displaying precious memories. Formal Dining separate from Formal Living Room. Large Guest Bedroom w/full Bath on the main floor. Large Master Bedroom with good outside lighting and rear view. Deluxe Master Bath has separate 5" Shower & 5" soaking Garden Tub. Large Walk-in-Closet & deluxe Bath 5' Shower, 5' Soaker Tub & Double Vanity. Nicely Tiled Floor. Luxurious Iron Railing Stairs leads to spacious open Loft on 2nd floor plus a must-see one of a kind custom built game room fitted with led lights, led floors & led control. Convenient Upstairs Laundry Room with Shelves. Walk-out Basement. Rear enclosed Deck overlooking private fenced-in backyard. The Community Features 2 Recreation areas with 2 separate Pools, Swim, Water Fountains, Tennis Courts, Basketball Court & Playground  with Playsets. Great North Forsyth School District! Nearby Popular Lake Lanier Beach Island and entertaining park. Great Metro Atlanta Location has everything!
